seal     : A party loses their swordsman's sister to a dragon deep in a labyrinth, and they're broke. So they go back in — and, to survive without supplies, they start cooking and eating the monsters. What sounds like a gag becomes a meticulous, warm study of an ecosystem, a found family, and what it means to live off a world rather than just conquer it.
